name: "rikawsdus"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
we were so scared because we thought Ricardus was mad and had gone mentally deranged but he was just starting to look for his Halloween costume.
our buddy is looking for a costume as stylish as he is, will Ricardus go out dressed as companion, the doll invented by Kaws?
